Title: Assault on the Airstrip
Description:
I have found their hidden airfield, $n: the Strongarm Airstrip. It wasn't hard to spot, it's swarming with Alliance.

<Nazgrim spits.>

They think they've wiped us out, but we're Horde! We fight until we're corpses... and sometimes even afterwards. Let them taste our steel!
ObjectivesText: Slay 15 Strongarm troops at Strongarm Airstrip.
